### Open SSE stream (curl-like in REST Client)
# REST Client doesn't support streaming SSE; this example shows the header usage for normal requests.

GET {{wordpress-mcp.url}}
Authorization: Bearer {{wordpress-mcp.token}}

### Example: call messages endpoint (JSON-RPC POST)
POST https://100blogs.ovh/30/index.php/wp-json/easy-visual-mcp/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{wordpress-mcp.token}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": { "tool": "mcp_ping", "args": {} },
  "id": 1
}
